ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend this program to another students. It definitely improved my language.

I would recommend it because for me this course worked very good and allowed to improve my English speaking skills. Moreover, it provides an opportunity to communicate with students from different cultures and with different backgrounds.
I would definitely recommend the course. The course is a great opportunity for preparing the students for being teaching assistants.
